fields.Title of Presentation: AVES MIGRATORIAS DE NORTE AMÉRICA: El Observatorio de Aves de Idaho (IBO)
fields.Conference/Meeting Name: Special Lecture for Fundacion Migres in Tarifa, Spain
fields.Description/Abstract: This was an invited lecture given (in Spanish!) at a community center in Tarifa, Spain while I was visiting the migration research of Fundacion Migres (collaboration with Boise State University and Idaho Bird Observatory).  I mostly covered our fall migration research but also touched on several of our other research projects.
